            <h1>ACLU Advocate Reining in Government Use of Face Surveillance, Champion of Privacy  Rights Research, and Data Security Trainer Protecting Black Communities Named Recipients of EFF’s Pioneer Award</h1>
    </div>
<div class="panel-pane pane-entity-field pane-node-field-pr-subhead">
            <div class="field field--name-field-pr-subhead field--type-text field--label-hidden"><div class="field__items"><div class="field__item even">Virtual Ceremony September 16 Will Honor Kade Crockford, Pam Dixon, and Matt Mitchell</div></div></div>    </div>
<div class="panel-pane pane-eff-content-type">
            PRESS RELEASE    </div>
<div class="panel-pane pane-eff-author">
            <div class="byline">Press Release</div><div class="date">August 23, 2021</div>    </div>
  </div>

